board of directors has concluded that mr howell due to his high level involvement can serve effectively in the dual role of chairman of the board and president and chief executive officer he is also chairman president and chief executive officer of gray television inc in addition to being very familiar with our company mr howell is also a licensed attorney which background provides additional perspective to the decisions facing not only our company but the board of directors mr howell has also been actively involved in various segments of the insurance industry throughout his career resulting in significant depth and breadth of industry knowledge which is beneficial to the board of directors mr howell is the soninlaw of mrs robinson and is also mrs howells husband source atlantic american corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view hilton h howell jrs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like hilton h howell jr more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in hilton h howell jrs network and community follow changes in hilton h howell jrs employment and moneyinmotion connect with hilton h howell jr through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example hilton h howell jr hilton h howell jrs connections  sign up now to view hilton h howell jrs  connections » mark e preisinger board member atlantic american corporation william h whaley former consultant atlantic american corporation hugh e norton board member gray television inc scott g thompson board member and president and ceo american southern insurance company board member and president and ceo and american southern insurance company atlantic american corporation robert a beizer former vice president law and development and secretary gray television inc harold k fischer former board member atlantic american corporation joseph m scheerer former board member 